---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy — streanga.com"
    description="What this site collects (almost nothing) and how contact-form messages are handled."
>
    <main id="main">
        <article class="legal container">
            <h1>Privacy</h1>
            <p class="updated">Last updated: 16 July 2026</p>

            <p>
                Short version: this site sets no tracking cookies, runs no
                analytics or ad networks, and collects nothing about you unless
                you choose to send me a message.
            </p>

            <h2>Theme preference</h2>
            <p>
                When you switch between light and dark mode, your choice is
                saved in your browser's <code>localStorage</code> under a
                <code>theme</code> key. It never leaves your device and is never sent
                anywhere. Clearing your browser's site data removes it.
            </p>

            <h2>Contact form</h2>
            <p>
                If you use the contact form, the email address, optional name,
                and message you submit are delivered to my personal inbox via <a
                    href="https://resend.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Resend</a
                >, an email delivery service, so that I can reply. That
                information is used only to respond to you; it is never sold,
                shared, or used for marketing, and I keep it about as long as
                I'd keep any email. Resend handles the message in transit under
                its own privacy policy.
            </p>

            <h2>Hosting &amp; delivery</h2>
            <p>
                The site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages and served over
                Cloudflare's network. Like any host or CDN, Cloudflare processes
                basic request data such as your IP address to deliver the site
                and protect it from abuse. I don't receive or store that beyond
                Cloudflare's standard logs.
            </p>

            <h2>No tracking</h2>
            <p>
                No analytics, no advertising, no third-party trackers, and no
                cookies beyond the functional theme preference above.
            </p>

            <h2>Questions</h2>
            <p>
                Reach me through the <a href="/#contact">contact form</a> or at <a
                    href="mailto:contactform@streanga.com"
                    >contactform@streanga.com</a
                >.
            </p>
        </article>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .legal {
        max-inline-size: 44rem;
        padding-block: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);
    }
    .legal h1 {
        font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
    .updated {
        margin-block-start: var(--space-3);
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }
    .legal h2 {
        margin-block-start: var(--space-12);
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
    .legal p {
        margin-block-start: var(--space-4);
    }
    .legal code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, "SFMono-Regular", Menlo, monospace;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
        background-color: var(--color-surface-sunken);
        border-radius: 4px;
    }
</style>
